                          Takes &lt; 2 mins
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="results-timeline centered-header">
            <h3>Start Seeing Results In 6 Months</h3>
            <div id="condition-timeline-container"></div>
          </div>
          <a
